Usage:
	time

This command will report the current day and time in the realm. The calendar
system is as follows.  Since this is a learning mud, the time is just an
example of what you can do with it.

	One year has 17 months, one for each of the deities.
	One month has 5 weeks, one for each of the Elder Gods.
	One week has 4 days, one for each of the elements.

	One year has 340 days. One month is 20 days.
